{"tid":1164173,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"部分 Pixel 3a 出現意外關機問題","createTime":"2019-05-21T01:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T13:03:29.000Z","uid":1121,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa9e2cdaa603b22ba20ad06b6f2d0c1360b746b","tid":1164173,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:39:54.000Z","msg":"定位中階的 Pixel 3a 和 Pixel 3a XL 發表至今已經一陣子，相信不少朋友也有入手一台，使用下來有沒有感覺到跟高階 Pixel 很相似呢？在有 bug 的部分。在Reddit 和 Google 支援頁面裡都有相當的聲音在投訴 Pixel 3a 系列有意外關機的問題，有的要重設原廠設定才能解決問題，但有更完全無法處理。我們已經向 Google 查詢事件，正等待回應。<br />\n<br />\n目前這問題仍未有明確的的原由，而且也不知道是什麼因素會觸發，只清楚 Pixel 3a 和 3a XL 都不能避免。有人更把手機嘗試以安全模式啟動，以確保並非第三方服務對系統有影響，但仍然出現關機問題，所以根源顯然是在 Google 的系統裡面。<br />\n<br />\n這並非 Google Pixel 手機產品首次出現事故，初代的 Pixel 曾出現麥克風問題、Pixel 2 更是有多個與品質監控相關的錯漏、Pixel 3 也有軟體相關的問題，而這次 Pixel 3a 系列暫時只是意外關機..."},{"pid":"5a56328992206ef4942eba901db895c9f662758d","tid":1164173,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:40:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2019/05/20/google-pixel-3a-and-3a-xl-random-shut-down-bug/?fbclid=IwAR08xS55tuHcnhe42cP0P56GorBrpAA3QVKrq22MP5Qj1J6nWO0fmP6ckjc#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2019%2F05%2F20%2Fgoogle-pixel-3a-and-3a-xl-random-shut-down-bug%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR08xS55tuHcnhe42cP0P56GorBrpAA3QVKrq22MP5Qj1J6nWO0fmP6ckjc%23&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=acfd76a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2019/05/20/google-pixel-3a-and-3a-xl-random-shut-down-bug/?fbclid=IwAR08xS55tuHcnhe42cP0P56GorBrpAA3QVKrq22MP5Qj1J6nWO0fmP6ckjc#</a>"},{"pid":"620db9e0ed222f0a6f13d771caedba213ad24345","tid":1164173,"uid":232197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:42:32.000Z","msg":"咁快有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a450956f1dde1b128bd78c9b3e758e8b94fd2db","tid":1164173,"uid":37688,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,